                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your triceps make up a large proportion of your upper arms. They aid your chest and shoulders in pressing movements and improve your elbow stability. </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re looking to build horseshoe-shaped muscle mass, the dumbbell overhead tricep extension is an excellent exercise. It works all three heads of your triceps and is easy to perform. </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our detailed guide below tells you everything you need to know. </span></p>                    </div>
